rComments: Extremely helpful teacher with lots of office hours. Has a foreign accent but that can be overcame easily as she speaks good English. The only problem is that her graders are inconsistent with her teaching which causes problems.
She is one of the best professors I have ever had!  The class is difficult, but she's always willing to help and extremely fair.
She goes right from the book. No need to go to class, except for midterms and final. Homework is posted online and can be handed in to her grader. Very easy class.
